## Threat Intelligence & ATT&CK

One of ATT&CK's most valuable uses is mapping Cyber Threat Intelligence (CTI) to known adversary behaviours.

This allows organizations to:

- Profile threat actors
- Understand common attack patterns
- Identify defensive gaps
- Build detections around known TTPs
- Improve incident investigations

By mapping activity to ATT&CK techniques, security teams can convert threat intelligence into actionable detection logic, SIEM rules, playbooks, and response procedures.

